@startuml
state WaitingForInput
state PredefinedAmounts
state CustomAmount
state CancelledTransaction

PredefinedAmounts --> WaitingForInput: Choose predefined amount
CustomAmount --> WaitingForInput: Input custom amount
WaitingForInput --> CustomAmount: User chooses custom amount
WaitingForInput --> PredefinedAmounts: User chooses predefined amount
WaitingForInput --> CancelledTransaction: User cancels transaction
CancelledTransaction --> ReturnCard: System stops transaction and returns card
@enduml
